-- Santander Brasil CEO mulls acquisitions to bolster growth in country
-- By Aluísio Alves
-- Mon Jun 23, 2014 09:54AM EDT
-- None



CAMPINAS, Brazil, June 23 (Reuters) - Banco Santander Brasil SA <SANB11.SA> will only consider acquisitions in sectors in which Brazil's third biggest private-sector lender plans to grow in coming years, Chief Executive Officer Jesús Zabalza said on Monday.

